    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes extensions to OSPFv3 to support intra-area Traffic Engineering (TE).  This document extends OSPFv2 TE to handle IPv6 networks.  A new TLV and several new sub-TLVs are defined to support IPv6 networks. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
